WEBVTT

00:07:59.747 --> 00:08:02.622
Luckily, this is a problem
even the laziest among us

00:08:02.646 --> 00:08:04.085
can help to solve.

00:08:04.109 --> 00:08:06.477
If you can swipe left or right,

00:08:06.501 --> 00:08:07.671
you can help.

00:08:08.235 --> 00:08:09.416
Map this morning

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:12.454
and influence life-changing
decisions this afternoon.

00:08:12.478 --> 00:08:16.731
Frontline health workers and humanitarians
are literally waiting for you.

00:08:17.155 --> 00:08:18.373
Thank you.